#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automated Sales Funnels</strong> – Maximize conversions with the "
"<strong>Marketing Automation App</strong>, guiding potential buyers "
"seamlessly from interest to purchase."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລະບົບການຂາຍແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong> – ເພີ່ມອັດຕາການສັ່ງຊື້ດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດ"
"ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong>, ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍນຳພາລູກຄ້າຈາກຄວາມສົນໃຈໄປສູ່ການຊື້ຢ່າງເປັນລະບົບ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Campaigns That Convert</strong> – Use the <strong>Email "
"Marketing App</strong> to send newsletters, promotions, and updates straight"
" to your customers' inboxes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຄມເປນອີເມລ໌ທີ່ສ້າງຍອດຂາຍ</strong> – ນຳໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມລ໌</"
"strong> ເພື່ອສົ່ງຂ່າວສານ, ໂປຣໂມຊັ່ນ ແລະ ຂໍ້ມູນອັບເດດໄປຫາລູກຄ້າໂດຍກົງ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.ir_ui_view_1661
msgid ""
"<strong>Find the perfect case for your phone – durable, stylish, and built "
"for everyday life.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຄົ້ນຫາເຄສທີ່ສົມບູນແບບສຳລັບໂທລະສັບຂອງທ່ານ – ທົນທານ, ທັນສະໄໝ ແລະ ອອກແບບມາເພື່ອຊີວິດປະຈ"
"ຳວັນ.</strong>"

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.ir_ui_view_1661
msgid "<strong>Japanese collection</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຄໍເລັກຊັນຍີ່ປຸ່ນ</strong>"

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>One-Click Confirmation:</strong> Review and confirm purchase orders "
"instantly."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຢືນຢັນໃນຄລິກດຽວ:</strong> ກວດສອບ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ໄດ້ທັນທີ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Seamless Supplier Communication:</strong> Send orders to your "
"supplier in just one click, ensuring smooth and timely fulfillment."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການສື່ສານກັບຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ສະດວກ:</strong> ສົ່ງຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ໄປຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານໃນຄລິກດຽວ, ເພື່ອໃ"
"ຫ້ໝັ້ນໃຈວ່າການຈັດການສິນຄ້າຈະເປັນໄປຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວ."

#. module: dropshipping
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:dropshipping.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Media Made Simple</strong> – Schedule and manage posts "
"effortlessly with the <strong>Social Marketing App</strong> to keep your "
"audience engaged."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ໂຊຊຽວມີເດຍທີ່ງ່າຍດາຍ</strong> – ວາງແຜນ ແລະ ຈັດການໂພສໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍດ້ວຍ "
"<strong>ແອັບການຕະຫຼາດໂຊຊຽວ</strong> ເພື່ອສ້າງການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມກັບລູກຄ້າ."

